{"arkId":"cl010116311","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010116311","modified ":"2026-03-11","title":"Tabati\u00e8re","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Tabati\u00e8re"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XV (1715-1774) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : vers 1740 - 1760","currentLocation":"Sully, [OArt] Salle 614 - Galerie Louis XV, Vitrine 11","room":"Salle 614, Aile Aile Sully, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1740,"endYear":1760,"imprecision":"vers","text":"Milieu du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Ducrollay, Jean-Charles","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"vers 1712","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"avant 1766","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""},{"label":"Liot","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Emailleur","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 6751","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"accessoire personnel, bo\u00eete, \u00e9tui","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Tabati\u00e8re rectangulaire en or \u00e9maill\u00e9 en plein et en couleurs, \u00e0 d\u00e9cor de sc\u00e8nes d\u0027enfants sur toutes les faces, d\u0027 apr\u00e8s Boucher. \r\nSur le couvercle : la p\u00eache sign\u00e9e Liot, repr\u00e9sentant un jeune couple entour\u00e9 d\u0027abrisseaux \u00e9maill\u00e9s de vert en basse-taille. \r\nSous la bo\u00eete : la chasse au canard, gar\u00e7on tirant sur un volatile et jeune femme assise en arri\u00e8re-plan. \r\nSur la b\u00e2te : la le\u00e7on de musique ; le chant ; le baise-main ; une berg\u00e8re lisant une partition.\r\nL\u0027\u00e9mailleur parisien Liot est cit\u00e9 dans l\u0027Almanach des Beaux-Arts de 1754. Les sc\u00e8nes du couercle et du dessous de la bo\u00eete sont directement tir\u00e9es de deux des huit panneaux des Arts et des Sciences peints entre 1750 et 1753 par Fran\u00e7ois Boucher.","inscriptions":"Poin\u00e7on : \r ; Lettre N (1753 - 1754) (Poin\u00e7on de maison commune : Dans le fond de la bo\u00eete, sur le revers du couvercle, sur le revers de la b\u00e2te)\r ; Poin\u00e7on de ma\u00eetre orf\u00e8vre (Dans le fond de la bo\u00eete, sur le revers du couvercle, sur le revers de la b\u00e2te)\r ; T\u00eate de boeuf (1750 - 1756) (Poin\u00e7on de charge : Dans le fond de la bo\u00eete, sur le revers du couvercle, sur le revers de la b\u00e2te)\r ; T\u00eate de poule (1750 - 1756) (Poin\u00e7on de d\u00e9charge : sur la gorge \u00e0 droite)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"3,7","displayDimension":"3,7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"8,1","displayDimension":"8,1 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"6","displayDimension":"6 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : or\r\nTechnique : \u00e9maill\u00e9 = \u00e9maillage = \u00e9mail = \u00e9maux (techniques m\u00e9tal)","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Charles Goding. Collection princesse de Wagram n\u00e9e Rothschild, vendue \u00e0 B de Schlichting 75.000 francs. Co